      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC is a survey of hosts to identify the implementation status of Telnet, FTP, and Mail on TCP.  The list of hosts was taken from the NIC hostname table of 2-Dec-82.  The tests were run on 14-Dec-82.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
